lockout-shortened 1999 season, averaging 1.6 points and 1.8 
rebounds per contest. His best year in the league was the 1993-94 
season, when he averaged 8.6 points and 8.3 rebounds as a starter 
for the Utah Jazz. 
</P>
<P>
